      "seed": 6001,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 6001,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1710849600000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "① TICKET PURCHASE\n   User → [sratix_tickets] → embed.js → Server/checkout\n   → Stripe Checkout → Stripe webhook → Server\n   → Issue tickets + Email + Badge render\n\n② CHECK-IN (QR)\n   Scanner → Server/check-ins/process-qr\n   → Verify HMAC → Update ticket → SSE → Dashboard\n\n③ MEMBER GATE\n   User → SRAtix Control (swiss-robotics.org)\n   → ProfileGrid auth → HMAC JWT → Server → Discounted price\n\n④ WEBHOOKS (Server → WP)\n   Server event → HMAC-sign → POST to sratix-client/v1/webhook\n   → Update WP options (maintenance, sold-out, etc.)\n\n⑤ OFFLINE SYNC\n   Mobile check-in (offline) → Batch POST → Server validates",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "① TICKET PURCHASE\n   User → [sratix_tickets] → embed.js → Server/checkout\n   → Stripe Checkout → Stripe webhook → Server\n   → Issue tickets + Email + Badge render\n\n② CHECK-IN (QR)\n   Scanner → Server/check-ins/process-qr\n   → Verify HMAC → Update ticket → SSE → Dashboard\n\n③ MEMBER GATE\n   User → SRAtix Control (swiss-robotics.org)\n   → ProfileGrid auth → HMAC JWT → Server → Discounted price\n\n④ WEBHOOKS (Server → WP)\n   Server event → HMAC-sign → POST to sratix-client/v1/webhook\n   → Update WP options (maintenance, sold-out, etc.)\n\n⑤ OFFLINE SYNC\n   Mobile check-in (offline) → Batch POST → Server validates",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

