    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "legend_text",
      "x": 1730,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 510,
      "height": 270,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 8001,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 8001,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1710849600000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "LEGEND\n\n🔵 Blue  — WordPress tier (sratix-client + Control)\n🟣 Purple — SRAtix Server (NestJS + Fastify)\n🟢 Green — Dashboard (Next.js 15 static SPA)\n🟡 Yellow — External services\n🔴 Red   — Database (MariaDB)\n\n── Solid arrow — Request/response (REST API)\n╌╌ Dashed arrow — Async (webhooks, SSE, jobs)\n⟷  Double arrow — Bidirectional (Redis, DB)\n\nServer: tix.swiss-robotics.org (port 3000)\nDashboard: Served as static export by Server",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "legend_box",
      "originalText": "LEGEND\n\n🔵 Blue  — WordPress tier (sratix-client + Control)\n🟣 Purple — SRAtix Server (NestJS + Fastify)\n🟢 Green — Dashboard (Next.js 15 static SPA)\n🟡 Yellow — External services\n🔴 Red   — Database (MariaDB)\n\n── Solid arrow — Request/response (REST API)\n╌╌ Dashed arrow — Async (webhooks, SSE, jobs)\n⟷  Double arrow — Bidirectional (Redis, DB)\n\nServer: tix.swiss-robotics.org (port 3000)\nDashboard: Served as static export by Server",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
